Establishments in and around the Hamilton CMA that serve food.

Source: R/envsocty3LT3-package.R
hamilton_sustenance.Rd

A table with establishments that serve food in and around the Hamilton CMA. These data were obtained from OpenStreetMap and includes the following types of establishments: Bar, Cafe, Fast Food, Food Court, Pub, and Restaurant. The object is projected as UTM Zone 17N.

data(hamilton_sustenance)

Format

A simple features object with 3,772 rows and 5 variables:

osm_id

Unique identifier for the point in OpenStreetMap

name

Name of establishment (when available)

amenity

Amenity category (when available). See: https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:amenity

type

Type of establishment: Bar, Cafe, Fast Food, Food Court, Pub, Restaurant

geometry

Geometry column

Source

OpenStreetMaps (https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=3/71.34/-96.82)
